*****************************************************************************************
*                 Bro Covert Channel Detection framework (BroCCaDe)                     *
*****************************************************************************************

V0.1.

This directory contains the source code and documentation for the Bro Covert
Channel Detection framework (BroCCaDe) framework. BroCCaDe consists of several
Bro plugin in the different sub directories. Please see the README files in the
plugin for more information on the different plugins.

Please see the file LICENSE for the information about the license BroCCaDe is
release under.

